<darkcolour>A6416E</darkcolour><section><title>Countable and uncountable nouns</title><sectiontitle>&lt;B&gt;Countable nouns&lt;/B&gt; have singular and plural forms. We can put a number in front of them.</sectiontitle><titlesound>ELEMGRAM_4_1_1.mp3</titlesound><text1>1 banana</text1><sound1>ELEMGRAM_4_1_2.mp3</sound1><text1a>&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;3&lt;/Font&gt; banana&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;s&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text1a><text2>1 egg</text2><sound2>ELEMGRAM_4_1_3.mp3</sound2><text2a>&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;25&lt;/Font&gt; egg&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;s&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text2a><titlesound2>ELEMGRAM_4_1_4.mp3</titlesound2><sectiontitle2>Use &lt;I&gt;How many...?&lt;/I&gt; with countable nouns.</sectiontitle2><text3>bananas</text3><sound3>ELEMGRAM_4_1_5.mp3</sound3><text3a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;How many&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; banana&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;s&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; do you buy every week?</text3a><text4>eggs</text4><sound4>ELEMGRAM_4_1_6.mp3</sound4><text4a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;How many&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; egg&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;s &lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;do you eat?</text4a></section><section><title>Countable and uncountable nouns</title><sectiontitle>&lt;B&gt;Uncountable nouns&lt;/B&gt; do not have plural forms. We cannot put a number in front of them. Use &lt;I&gt;How much...?&lt;/I&gt; with uncountable nouns.</sectiontitle><titlesound>ELEMGRAM_4_1_7.mp3</titlesound><text1>water</text1><sound1>ELEMGRAM_4_1_8.mp3</sound1><text1a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;How much&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; water do you drink every day?</text1a><text2>rice</text2><sound2>ELEMGRAM_4_1_9.mp3</sound2><text2a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;How much&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; rice do you buy every week?</text2a><titlesound2>%undefined</titlesound2><sectiontitle2>%undefined</sectiontitle2><text3>%undefined</text3><sound3>%undefined</sound3><text3a>%undefined</text3a><text4>%undefined</text4><sound4>%undefined</sound4><text4a>%undefined</text4a></section></grammar>